org.apache.hadoop.hbase.io.compress

Interface CanReinit

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BrotliCompressor, HadoopCompressor, Lz4Codec.HadoopLz4Compressor, Lz4Compressor, LzoCodec.HadoopLzoCompressor, SnappyCodec.HadoopSnappyCompressor, SnappyCompressor, ZstdCodec.HadoopZstdCompressor, ZstdCompressor, ZstdDecompressor

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public interface CanReinit
    This is a marker interface that indicates if a compressor or decompressor type can support reinitialization via reinit(Configuration conf).
